                ".52",
                ".56",
                ".62"
            ],
            "correct_response": [
                [
                    "2"
                ]
            ],
            "solution": "<div><B>Solution: <br>Correct\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAnswer : <b>2</B>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>log 24 = log (2\u00d72\u00d72\u00d73) = 3 log 2 + log 3 = 1.48<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlog 54 = log (2\u00d73\u00d73\u00d73) = log 2 + 3 log 3 = 1.56<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBy simplifying these two equations, we get<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t4 log2 + 4 log3 = 3.04\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br> i.e, 2 log2 + 2 log 3 = 1.52\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div></div>"
        },
